{"tid":1071451,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"對人生已經充滿絕望","createTime":"2019-03-21T11:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T15:12:22.000Z","uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"97e3b9501671184211b2e5face9de98807c3f652","tid":1071451,"uid":195975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:00:10.000Z","msg":"愈黎愈灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569183f1417c64e8fe87b647bd5912fad471c4d7","tid":1071451,"uid":106326,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:09:20.000Z","msg":"其實有事真係自己既原因唔開心定環境影響下唔開心<br />\n<br />\n成日都話香港係最唔開心既城市之一<br />\n之後舉出一大堆數據去證明香港地做人到底有幾痛苦<br />\n<br />\n如果我知我係因為返工太辛苦或者買唔到樓唔開心<br />\n我都可以懶落環境度 等自己心理平衡啲<br />\n<br />\n但有時會唔會係 其實就算依家比你係第二個國家生活<br />\n個人一樣都係會充滿著悲觀<br />\n<br />\n個人已經灰心到其實有冇事發生都好 當一靜落黎就會諗「做人真係好辛苦」<br />\n到底呢個先係都市病 抑或係我係度生活左咁多年而累積既精神病？"},{"pid":"46e04af8ff6303f563c3c94b37cf579b7414c2e1","tid":1071451,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:09:51.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"28dac3126e6f1f7f726af5dd98f390c1c124d0dd","tid":1071451,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:09:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f462beff2ae080c219fadb2393be79dfcf592c5","tid":1071451,"uid":173075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:10:52.000Z","msg":"same here ，可以做d咩好 係踢波既時候最開心 靜返個人就好sad"},{"pid":"c4dd47acc728233c3461b7b93532ba0923a87a8a","tid":1071451,"uid":44184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f462beff2ae080c219fadb2393be79dfcf592c5","tid":1071451,"uid":173075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:10:52.000Z","msg":"same here ，可以做d咩好 係踢波既時候最開心 靜返個人就好sad"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:14:45.000Z","msg":"但當你踢唔到時...."},{"pid":"b4821cce2832a5e8e1a77c0d89